e&#8217;re pleased to announce our recently launched plugin, Keyy, has just passed the 1000 user milestone. Keyy was inspired by the now deprecated Clef and makes logging into WordPress sites with a smartphone simple and secure.  Only someone with your phone &#8230; <a href="https://updraftplus.com/keyy-two-factor-plugin-surges-past-1000-users/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com/keyy-two-factor-plugin-surges-past-1000-users/">Keyy Two Factor Plugin surges past 1000 users</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href="http://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"Joe Miles";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2024:"<p>We&#8217;re pleased to announce our recently launched plugin, <a href="https://getkeyy.com">Keyy</a>, has just passed the 1000 user milestone.</p>\n<p>Keyy was inspired by the now deprecated Clef and makes logging into WordPress sites with a smartphone simple and secure.  Only someone with your phone and passcode can login to your sites making it ultra secure.  But it&#8217;s much simpler than traditional two factor authentication as it simply involves scanning the Keyy wave with our iOS or Android app.</p>\n<p>Since launch, Keyy has received great reviews from industry publications such as News47ell (<a href="https://www.news47ell.com/reviews/keyy-two-factor-authentication-review">https://www.news47ell.com/reviews/keyy-two-factor-authentication-review</a>) as well as strong feedback from early adopters who are keen to see more:</p>\n<p><em><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Screen-Shot-2017-08-07-at-11.32.50.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223197" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Screen-Shot-2017-08-07-at-11.32.50.png" alt="" width="586" height="372" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Screen-Shot-2017-08-07-at-11.32.50.png 586w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Screen-Shot-2017-08-07-at-11.32.50-300x190.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Screen-Shot-2017-08-07-at-11.32.50-510x324.png 510w" sizes="(max-width: 586px) 100vw, 586px" /></a></em></p>\n<p>Keyy has been undergoing regular releases and we&#8217;re looking forward to announcing some other exciting updates soon.</p>\n<span class="et_bloom_bottom_trigger"></span><p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com/keyy-two-factor-plugin-surges-past-1000-users/">Keyy Two Factor Plugin surges past 1000 users</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href="http://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:75:"https://updraftplus.com/keyy-two-factor-plugin-surges-past-1000-users/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:70:"https://updraftplus.com/keyy-two-factor-plugin-surges-past-1000-users/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_